LAGOS – Music is a universal language that everyone understands and where words fail music speaks.For Samuel Enyi, whose stage name is DJ Irem$, life is music and music is life. He is an artiste who wants to create a unique sound by fusing Afrobeat, Amapiano, House Music and Afrodancehall into an inimitable sound that will appeal to music lovers of all generations. He speaks with the music when he is on the wheel of steel and keeps the crowd going at every point in time with his skilful command of rotation of sound choice. He has done this very well in his recent selection of features and collaborations. DJ Irem$ can’t go wrong when he is on the wheels of steel whenever he entertains his audience.Speaking with him recently about his love and drive for music, he stated that music is an art and is spiritual to him.